---

Design Principles Applied

Encapsulation: All statistics are private and modifiable only through dedicated methods.

Single Responsibility Principle: The class focuses solely on statistics tracking and reporting.

Modularity: Allows easy reuse for both player and enemy roosters.



---

Future Enhancements

Percentage-based performance analysis

Battle rating system (e.g., S/A/B/C)

Graphical (GUI-based) statistics report

Export stats to file for logging

Support for multi-round tournaments



